  "description": "Add a dedicated iOS 26 Search tab (Tab(role: .search)) that performs live debounced full-text article search against GET /articles/search. A new APIClient.searchArticles method provides the network layer; a new SearchView handles all UI states (Idle, Loading, Empty, Error, Not Configured, Loaded) with debounce and cursor pagination; AppRoot wires in the tab. Results reuse ArticleRowView \u2192 ArticlePagerView, preserving all existing read/save behaviour. No sort control \u2014 results stay in backend relevance order.",
